node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Keep On Learning on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Usain Bolt won 8 gold medals in 3 Olympics, and he only ran for less than 115 seconds on the track, earning $119 million dollars. That's economy of effort. But for those 2 minutes, he trained for 20 years. That's investment. Think long term. Patience pays. 1003 2163 3317'.
